Echo v1.4.1 - no countdown, longer speech, Echo stops shooting

- Remove countdown timer: no time limit, Echo just gets worse
- Speech bubbles linger 5s (was 2s) with 1.2s fade out (was 0.6s)
- Echo no longer shoots: it is not trying to kill you
- Echo dodges and strafes evasively instead of attacking
- HUD shows how long Echo has been alive (not a countdown)
- Slogan: YOU BETTER KILL IT FAST... OR UNINSTALL!
- Title screen flavor text updated for new mechanic
- Round end always shows kill time, no fail state
